    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 inline-six, featuring factory individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system recently overhauled with Beisan components for peak volumetric efficiency. This example boasts a reinforced rear subframe and a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox with precise synchronizer engagement. Power is managed via the variable M Differential Lock, providing exceptional lateral grip. The chassis remains taut on OEM Bilstein dampers, with zero bushing deflection or fluid leaks. Finished in original paint with immaculate Nappa leather, this is a mechanically transparent, turn-key masterpiece for the purist.",
